    <item>
      <title>杰富瑞希望向公司创始人乔治·韦斯支付款项</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-07/jefferies-wants-payments-to-firm-founder-george-weiss-reviewed</link>
      <description><![CDATA[杰富瑞金融集团 (Jefferies Financial Group) 要求对乔治·韦斯在今年早些时候申请破产之前可能从其同名投资公司 Weiss Multi-Strategy Advisers 收到的任何付款进行独立审查。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-07/jefferies-wants-payments-to-firm-founder-george-weiss-reviewed</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 07 Aug 2024 16:08:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国、北约谴责科索沃计划重开重要桥梁，引发塞族抗议</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-07/us-nato-slam-kosovo-plan-to-reopen-key-bridge-as-serbs-protest</link>
      <description><![CDATA[西方伙伴呼吁科索沃停止重新开放阿尔巴尼亚族和塞尔维亚族社区之间河流上重要桥梁的计划，因为这可能会重新引发巴尔干国家北部的紧张局势。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-07/us-nato-slam-kosovo-plan-to-reopen-key-bridge-as-serbs-protest</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 07 Aug 2024 16:06:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Meta 的目标是 105 亿美元，这是其最大的高等级债券销售</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-07/meta-meta-kicks-off-bond-sale-as-companies-storm-high-grade-market</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Meta Platforms Inc. 正在发行价值 105 亿美元的投资级债券，这是其有史以来最大规模的债券发行，这将增加其现金储备，因为该公司正在大力投资人工智能。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-07/meta-meta-kicks-off-bond-sale-as-companies-storm-high-grade-market</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 07 Aug 2024 12:37:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>布鲁克菲尔德资产利润未达预期，资产规模达到约 1 万亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-07/brookfield-asset-management-profits-rise-assets-hit-1-trillion</link>
      <description><![CDATA[布鲁克菲尔德资产管理有限公司 (Brookfield Asset Management Ltd.) 表示，其管理的资产增至创纪录的约 1 万亿美元，并报告利润较上年同期有所增加，但仍低于分析师的预期。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-07/brookfield-asset-management-profits-rise-assets-hit-1-trillion</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 07 Aug 2024 11:19:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
